{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji28","name":"毛泽东全集第28卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/maoquanji28.pdf"],"article":{"title":"给张四维的信","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"给张四维的信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1950年5月8日）四维兄："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一月十六日来信收到。吾兄已在盐业公司获得职业，甚好，应就此项工作努力，取得成绩与信任，不要来北京。北京人浮于事，不好安置。前已复一信，未知收到否？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顺祝进步！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五月八日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[1]张四维（1892—1961），湖南省韶山市韶山乡韶山村人。大革命时期曾参加韶山农民运动。新中国成立后，在中国盐业公司湖南省公司工作。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1950,"month":5,"day":8}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":358,"page_end":358},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"书信"}]}]}